    colorTheme: 2
  - title: 'FlipBook Player:'
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1886
      y: 2502
      width: 369
      height: 142
    contents: 'The Flipbook Player allows you to easily animate your flipbook or
      sprite sheet.

      Just give a frame rate and the block does the rest for
      you.

      In the background, this block is updating the texIndex value to
      animate the frame:

      texIndex +=  frameRate * delta Time ;

'
    theme: 
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 3
